 288:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      When the compilation flag USE_HAL_ADC_REGISTER_CALLBACKS is set to 0 or
 289:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      not defined, the callback registration feature is not available and all callbacks
