3438:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         defined as it impacts the ADC LSB equivalent voltage.
3439:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Analog reference voltage (Vref+) must be either known from
3440:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         user board environment or can be calculated using ADC measurement
3441:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and ADC helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CALC_VREFANALOG_VOLTAGE().
3442:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, calibration data of temperature sensor
