3490:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                                   (unit: uV/Degree Celsius)
3491:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_TYP_CALx_VOLT = temperature sensor digital value at
3492:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                                   temperature CALx_TEMP (unit: mV)
3493:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve the temperature sensor
3494:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  of the current device has characteristics in line with
3495:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  datasheet typical values.
