4833:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - For devices with sequencer not fully configurable
4834:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (function "LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerChannels()" available):
