4837:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This function retrieves:
4838:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence length: Number of ranks in the scan sequence is
4839:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             defined by number of channels set in the sequence,
4840:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             rank of each channel is fixed by channel HW number.
4841:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             (channel 0 fixed on rank 0, channel 1 fixed on rank1, ...).
