5207:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC conversions) is reached.
5208:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This ADC mode is intended to be used with DMA mode non-circular.
5209:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Unlimited mode: DMA transfer requests are unlimited,
