5218:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   For devices with several ADC instances: ADC multimode DMA
5219:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         settings are available using function @ref LL_ADC_SetMultiDMATransfer().
