7496:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
7497:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC multimode delay between 2 sampling phases.
7498:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The sampling delay range depends on ADC resolution:
7499:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC resolution 12 bits can have maximum delay of 12 cycles.
7500:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC resolution 10 bits can have maximum delay of 10 cycles.
7501:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC resolution  8 bits can have maximum delay of  8 cycles.
7502:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC resolution  6 bits can have maximum delay of  6 cycles.
7503:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
7504:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
7505:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         All ADC instances of the ADC common group must be disabled.
7506:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This check can be done with function @ref LL_ADC_IsEnabled() for each
7507:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC instance or by using helper macro helper macro
7508:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref __LL_ADC_IS_ENABLED_ALL_COMMON_INSTANCE().
7509:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CCR      DELAY          LL_ADC_SetMultiTwoSamplingDelay
7510:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCxy_COMMON ADC common instance
7511:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (can be set directly from CMSIS definition or by using helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_COMMO
7512:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  MultiTwoSamplingDelay This parameter can be one of the following values:
7513:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_MULTI_TWOSMP_DELAY_1CYCLE
7514:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_MULTI_TWOSMP_DELAY_2CYCLES
7515:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_MULTI_TWOSMP_DELAY_3CYCLES
